<title>PC.Stats.CharacterStats Class Reference</title>
<indexterm><primary>PC.Stats.CharacterStats</primary></indexterm>
<para>

<para>This class is used to store general stats and damage behavior common to all game characters.  </para>
 
</para>
<simplesect>
    <title>Public Member Functions    </title>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem><para><anchor xml:id="_class_p_c_1_1_stats_1_1_character_stats_1adf381679b61e65aa1bc320d35f92e666"/>void <emphasis role="strong">TakeDamage</emphasis> ()</para>

<para>The general damage function. This is called by other scripts any time the relevant entity needs to lose health points.  </para>
</listitem>
            <listitem><para>virtual void <link linkend="_class_p_c_1_1_stats_1_1_character_stats_1a6c3192bd5552f52b8bb430c2f5c223b5">Die</link> ()</para>

<para>Logs an entities death to the console. Specific death behavior and animations will be defined in scripts specific to a character.  </para>
</listitem>
